				I have made a blog myself. It is about finding companies in the UK to donate goods to the tsunami children. If you know of any people here or in the US who will donate toys and teddies that can help to make them smile a little bit they can contact me or my mum please. Please have a look at my blog and leave a link to yours too. My blog address is www.donatetotsunami.blogspot.com <br />Thankyou very much!<br />
